Downloaded from:  https://www.michaelwimmer.org/downloads.html  on 260421  (tried also https://github.com/xrq-phys/Pfapack but had some subtle bugs)


cd fortran; cp makefile.gnu/intel/aris makefile; make clean; make


--------------------------------------------------------------------------
For Pfaffian:  (interfaces to allt types s/d/c/z f77 routines)
skpfa.f90  : use f95_pfapack; call skpfa (M,pfaf)    M(:,:), scalar pfaff
skpf10.f90 : use f95_pfapack; call skpf10(M,pfaff)   M(:,:),        pfaff(2)   pfaffian = pfaff(1) * 10**pfaff(2) 

--------------------------------------------------------------------------
